name: Fossil Neutra Minimalist Multifunction Watch
description: Fossil Neutra Minimalist FS5903 is a practical and handsome Gents watch. Case material is Stainless Steel and the Blue dial gives the watch that unique look. This model has got 50 metres water resistancy - it can be submerged in water for periods, so can be used for swimming and fishing. It is not recommended for high impact water sports. We ship it with an original box and a guarantee from the manufacturer.

name: Swatch Portrait Of Dedie Pompidou Watch
description: This Swatch art collaboration watch celebrates the painting 'The Portrait of Dédie' by Amedeo Modigliani, by placing the portrait itself in the centre of the silver dial with multi-colored print. This Swatch X Centre Pompidou Collection watch also features Amedeo Modigliani's signature on the 12 o’clock strap, which is a first for Swatch. A touch of pink on the transparent shiny plastic case and buckle soften the dark tones of the semi-transparent matte milky silicone strap.

name: Seiko Prospex Speedtimer Solar Chronograph Watch
description: The shape of the 39mm case keeps true to the original but at the same time has a modern feel with a combination of smooth and hairline polishing on the bracelet, and the curved sapphire glass. The dial is extremely legible thanks to it's sandblasted finish, so has that crucial readability that is so important for a Prospex sports watch. This watch is powered by V192 Calibre solar movement, features a 60 minute chronograph inside a subdial at 6 o'clock, a 24 hour indicator and a time of the day seconds hand.

name: Swatch Blue Sky Pompidou Watch
description: This Swatch art collaboration watch celebrates Vassily Kandinsky's 'Blue Sky' painting with a semi-transparent matte light blue silicone strap featuring a multi-colored allover print based on his painting. The light blue continues onto the semi-transparent matte plastic case as well as the silicone loop and buckle. The dots at the tips of the hour and minute hands of this piece offer a subtle nod to the artist that art lovers will appreciate.
